		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#2c62d3" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#2c62d3">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="428" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">巨鲸缓慢冒出水面，在水面上缓慢进行游动，每往下游动，就会对周围造成伤害，该技能大概率重复2次；<br/>游动时，巨鲸冒出与触碰地面均造成<span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害，同时在此范围的周围产生6个喷溅延波，延波爆破造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="543" width="428" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">巨鲸从水面突然钻出，翻身后跌入水面下沉；<br/>游动时，巨鲸冒出与触碰地面均造成<span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害，同时在此范围的周围产生6个喷溅延波，延波爆破造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="428" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">巨鲸扎入水面，一段时间后再从水面突出游走，该技能顺序可颠倒；<br/>扎入和突出时，巨鲸触碰地面即造成<span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害，同时在此范围的周围产生8个胎水涌泉，胎水涌泉造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1412" y="543" width="422" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">巨鲸贴近水面，喷涌于空中，降下大量的星汐弹，均造成<span color="#7fbfff">30%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="831" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">巨鲸扎入水面，水映公子的鲸天座，降下数束魔光流注，流注命中造成<span color="#7fbfff">50%,<br/>25%</span><span>伤害，持续流注造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">12.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/吞星之鲸.assets/Image_14.png')" x="719" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
