		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/吞星之鲸.assets/Image_28.png')" x="1248" y="470" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/吞星之鲸.assets/Image_29.png')" x="596" y="779" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/吞星之鲸.assets/Image_30.png')" x="576" y="758" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="831" width="432" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">巨鲸将以不定周期召唤<span textDecoration="underline">涡眼</span><span>，其将持续牵引在场玩家，未及时处理将爆炸造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害；一阶段满</span><span textDecoration="underline">敌意</span><span>时或三阶段经过了30s后，若生命值&gt;20%，巨鲸将吞噬玩家，进入神秘空间，即二阶段。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
